description:
Welcome to this online personal goal setting course, SHAPE Your Future. The simple lessons with the accompanying exercises will guide you to a better and clearer understanding of your desires and help you with personal goal setting.

This personal goal setting course is designed to take you on a journey into your future and leave you with clear steps of action to take to set you on your way.

Here is the course outline:

SHAPE is an acronym meaning:
S for Searching out the clues,
H for Hearing your inner voice  
A for Analyzing the evidence  
P for Picturing from an new Perspective
E for Enacting the new game of life

Enjoy two FREE downloadable e-books: "The 3 Keys to Dissolving Fear" and "Your Invisbale Power"

Take the step towards personal goal setting today!
title: SHAPE Your Future
